Titolo: Carriers at War

Anno: 1984

Descrizione: Carriers at War 1941-1945: Fleet Carrier Operations in the Pacific is a 1984 computer wargame by Strategic Studies Group for Apple II and Commodore 64. The game was designed by Roger Keating and Ian Trout. A remake, Carriers at War, was released for MS-DOS in 1992. A sequel to the remake, Carriers at War II, was released for MS-DOS and Mac OS in 1993. A second remake was published by Matrix Games in 2007 for Microsoft Windows.